WEBVTT

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:30.696
and so we buckled ourselves in,

00:05:30.720 --> 00:05:32.054
and I dropped the last dose.

00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:37.216
As my brain experienced life
without prescription opioids

00:05:37.240 --> 00:05:38.640
for the first time in months,

00:05:40.360 --> 00:05:41.600
I thought I would die.

00:05:42.680 --> 00:05:43.936
I assumed I would die --

00:05:43.960 --> 00:05:45.016
(Crying)

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:46.256
I'm sorry.

00:05:46.280 --> 00:05:48.200
(Crying)

00:05:52.840 --> 00:05:55.080
Because if the symptoms
didn't kill me outright,

00:05:55.920 --> 00:05:57.120
I'd kill myself.

00:05:58.360 --> 00:06:00.216
And I know that sounds dramatic,